=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
לוה / lâvâh / law-vaw'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 
=== Verb ===
properly to [[twine]], that is, (by implication) to [[unite]], to remain; also to borrow (as a form of obligation) or (causatively) to lend: - abide with, borrow (-er), cleave, join (self), lend (-er).
[[fr:לוה]]